video_title: Basement Phil - Flying (The Deeper Side Mix)
description:
Before this track was reworked into Music Is So Special by Brothers With Soul (with the help of LTJ Bukem), this was how it sounded, very subtle and somewhat laying the blueprint for the  atmospheric style that was to originate from club nights like Speed.

Feel free to check out my other YouTube channels.

Somes notes about this rip. 

The record is pretty worn, so there are some very significant crackles. One channel is so bad that it has a persistant crackle throughout the entire 8.5 minute song. For this reason I had to drop the right channel and clone the left channel (ie. made it mono) for it to be listenable.The bass seems to come through really strangely as well...

Despite the shortcomings of this rip I decided to upload it anyway considering this is a great song and the current best rip is only 240p.
